title: Episode 511 - Rosanne Cash
itunes:title: Episode 511 - Rosanne Cash
description:
In the world of country music, the last name Cash holds a lot of weight. Rosanne Cash tells Marc how she paved her way in the music industry, how she bounced back after hitting the wall, and how she learned to cope with the long shadow cast by The Man In Black.
